							<span class="tag-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/blair" rel="tag">Blair</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/drake" rel="tag">Drake</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/espionage" rel="tag">espionage</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/foi" rel="tag">FoI</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/intelligence-2" rel="tag">intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/nsa" rel="tag">NSA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/obama" rel="tag">Obama</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/osa" rel="tag">OSA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/spies-2" rel="tag">spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/transparency" rel="tag">transparency</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/whistleblowers-2" rel="tag">whistleblowers</a>			</span>
						
